{"tid":2439391,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子投擲膠樽 蘇文隆採半年量刑起點 判監4個月","createTime":"2021-03-09T08:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T09:52:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"15dd4275c5c381deb5df677a83d740538d185deb","tid":2439391,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:28:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14264&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=d19b0ebd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14264</a><br />\n<br />\n#粉嶺裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#蘇文隆主任裁判官<br />\n#20200509大埔 #判刑<br />\n<br />\n黃<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序的行為<br />\n<br />\n控罪詳情：<br />\n於2020年5月9日，在大埔安邦路8及10號大埔超級城內，在公眾地方作擾亂秩序行為，即向警務人員投擲一個膠樽，意圖激使他人破壞社會安寧。<br />\n<br />\n🔴被告認罪🔴<br />\n<br />\n(詳情後補...)<br />\n<br />\n被告認為量刑起點過重，指將會就刑期進行上訴，並申請期間保釋，但蘇文隆認為被告的上訴並無任何合理理據，故拒絕其保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n‼️ 判處4個月即時監禁‼️<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},{"pid":"8d3e4179d47acbac573a7d86bb39e0db7cf30b9a","tid":2439391,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:30:29.000Z","msg":"在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序的行為<br />\n<br />\n半年 CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821a8c655a60dd36720666e45e1b47c6990afbf8","tid":2439391,"uid":34811,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:32:07.000Z","msg":"dom個膠樽都攞非法集結做量刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姓蘇果啲都係狗嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ba965aa2ebccd13db4462f5a4ecfd037f0475c","tid":2439391,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:32:47.000Z","msg":"見到蘇文隆已經唔洗睇實重判而且無野可以做到"},{"pid":"b616c489a5c5c960ff3be06ea1af6d3b460c4457","tid":2439391,"uid":321059,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:33:30.